                  <additions>
                     <list>
                       <item xml:id="a1">
                         <locus from="1v" to="3v"/>
                         <locus from="55vb" to="59r"/>
                         <desc type="GuestText"><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2999RepCh279">Malkǝʿa-hymn to John the Baptist, written in a very crude hand (that most probably wrote also 
                           other notes listed below)</title></desc>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">
                           በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ እሳት፡ በሐቅለ፡ ሕሊና፡ ነዳዲ፨ 
                           ወበስመ፡ ማርያም፡ ድንግል፡ መጥበቢተ፡ ዓለም፡ አባዲ፨ ማኅቶተ፡ ጥበብ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ <sic resp="DN">ጸልመተ፡ </sic>አበሳ፡ ሳዳዲ፨ ከመ፡ እዜኑ፡ ኂሩተከ፡ ዕዳ፡ ኃጣውዕየ፡ ይፍዲ፨ 
                         </q>
                       </item>
                       
                       <item xml:id="a2">
                         <desc type="OwnershipNote">The name of <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13952Heristoforos">Hǝristo Foros</persName> is indicated in supplications
                           in margins of most folia, in varying spelling (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ህሪስቶፎሮስ፡</foreign>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ህሪስቶፍሮ፡</foreign>;
                           <foreign xml:lang="gez">ህሪስቶፎሮ፡ ኤሳ</foreign>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ህሪስቶፎሮስ፡ ኤሳ፡ ደቂቁ፡ ለሳባ፡</foreign>).</desc>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">ለገብርከ፡ ህሪስቶ፡ ፎሮስ፡</q>
                       </item>
                       
                       <item xml:id="a3">
                         <desc type="Gloss">Explanation of the word <foreign xml:lang="gez">ቃሜላ፡</foreign> in the upper margin, referring to Mark 10:25.</desc>
                         <q xml:lang="am">ቃሜላ፡ ብሒል፡ የመርከብ፡ ገመድ፡ የመልህቁ፡</q>
                       </item>
                       
                       <item xml:id="a4">
                         <locus target="#53r"/>
                         <desc type="Supplication">Supplication written in the upper margin.</desc>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">በዝ፡ ቃለከ፡ ኢይቅርቡ፡ ሰይጣናት፡</q>
                       </item>
                       
                       <item xml:id="a5">
                         <locus target="#54r"/>
                         <desc type="Supplication">Supplication written in the upper margin.</desc>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">ኦእግዚዕየ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ህሪስቶስ፡ ፈውስ፡ ደውየሁ፡ ለሀጥዕ፡ ገብርከ፡ ህሪስቶፎሮ፡</q>
                       </item>
                       
                       <item xml:id="a6">
                         <locus target="#59r"/>
                         <desc type="Unclear">Indication of the chapter numbers.</desc>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">እሮም፡ ማቴዎስ፡ ፳፰፡ ማርቆስ፡ <del rend="erasure">፳</del>፲፮፡ ሉቃስ፡ ፳፬፡ ዮሕዐንስ፡ ፳፩</q>
                       </item>
                       
                       <item xml:id="e1">
                         <locus target="#1r"/>
                         <desc>Beginning of <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2999RepCh279">Malkǝʾa Yoḥannǝs Maṭmǝq</ref>, maybe pen trial.</desc>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ እሳት <t:gap xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="illegible"/>ቅለ፡ ሕሊናተ፡</q>
                       </item>
                       
                       <item xml:id="e2">
                         <desc>The "Coptic" and Greek (<foreign xml:lang="gez">በሮም፡</foreign>) numeration of chapters is given within the main body of the text.</desc>
                       </item>
                       
                       <item xml:id="e3">
                         <locus target="#1r #30v"/>

                         <desc>The days of the week are indicated in the upper margin. Kamil indicates the further division into the days of the week as 
                         follows: Monday: <locus target="#4r"/>, chapters 1-10; Tuesday: <locus target="#14r"/>, chapters 11-17;
                         Wednesday: <locus target="#21v"/>, chapters 18-27; Thursday: <locus target="#30v"/>, chapters 28-37;
                         Friday: <locus target="#37v"/>, chapters 38-45; Saturday: <locus target="#44r"/>, chapters 46-47;
                         Sunday: <locus target="#51r"/>, chapter 48.</desc>
                         
                       </item>
                       
                       <item xml:id="e4">
                         <locus target="#4r"/>
                         <desc>The name of <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13953Gabreel">Gabrǝʾel</persName> has been inserted probably after the production of the manuscript
                           in space left empty in the introductory supplication to <ref target="#ms_i1"/>. Later, it has been crossed out and that of 
                           <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13952Heristoforos">Hǝristo Foros</persName> has been added in the margin. In the final supplication on <locus target="#53ra"/>, the original 
                           name has been erased and that of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13952Heristoforos">Hǝristo Foros</persName> been written above the erasure.</desc>
                       </item>
                     </list>
                  </additions>

